H.P. 1169 House of Representatives, April 22, 2025
Reference to the Committee on State and Local Government suggested and ordered printed.
ROBERT B. HUNT
Clerk
Presented by Representative ROBERTS of South Berwick.
Cosponsored by Representatives: COLLAMORE of Pittsfield, EATON of Deer Isle, HEPLER
of Woolwich, MASTRACCIO of Sanford, SALISBURY of Westbrook, Senators: BENNETT
of Oxford, BRADSTREET of Kennebec, GROHOSKI of Hancock.
