35 amended to read:
36 9. Growth management program. "Growth management program" means a
37 document containing the components described in section 4326, including the
38 implementation program, that is consistent with the procedures, goals and guidelines
39 established by subchapter II 2 and that regulates land use beyond that required by Title 38,
40 chapter 3, subchapter I 1, article 2‑B.
