24 §4317. Adopted comprehensive plan in effect
25 A comprehensive plan adopted or amended by a municipality or multimunicipal region
26 under this subchapter remains in effect until amended or repealed in accordance with the
27 procedures, goals and guidelines established in this subchapter.
