34 Sec. 34. 30-A MRSA §4347-A, sub-§2, ¶B, as amended by PL 2011, c. 655, Pt.
35 JJ, §21 and affected by §41, is further amended to read:
36 B. Certification by the former State Planning Office or the department of a
37 municipality's or multimunicipal region's growth management program under this
38 article is valid for 10 12 years. To maintain certification, a municipality or
39 multimunicipal region shall periodically review its growth management program and
40 submit to the department in a timely manner any revisions necessary to account for
41 changes, including changes caused by growth and development. Certification does not
Page 11 - 132LR1666(01)
