4 Maine Revised Statutes, Title 30-A, chapter 187 that is submitted to the Department of
5 Agriculture, Conservation and Forestry for a consistency review within 24 months after the
6 final adoption of rules necessary to implement the provisions of this Act unless the relevant
7 municipality or multimunicipal region specifically requests that this Act be applied to that
8 municipality's or multimunicipal region's submission and the department authorizes that
9 application.
10 SUMMARY
1111 This bill makes changes to the laws governing municipal growth management
1122 programs by updating terminology and growth management program elements and
1133 procedures and requiring needs assessment, the addressing of local goals and a future land
1144 use plan as part of the comprehensive plan. The bill also clarifies the required components
1155 of future land use plans.
